extendedInfo.description: Inspire, Educate and Entertain! Best Animal Sounds and Animal Education Video App for Kids from Toddler to Teens and Animal Lovers of Any Age. Learn animal names, sounds, habitat and characters on top quality, hand picked free YouTube videos from BBC, PBS, Disney etc. Travel with the animals to its native environment in the Jungle of Asia, desert of Africa and icy Arctic circle...   Guarantee you and your loved kids have a great time and leave a big smile on your face!Features:-Awesome animal sounds-Professionally recorded animal names and wonderful animal pictures-Hand picked, top quality, kids friendly animal educational YouTube videos-The only App that offers top quality animal videos from  BBC, PBS, Disney.-Travel with the animal to its native environment in the forest, desert, arctic or the ocean of Africa, Asia, Australia, Europe, America and all parts of the planet.-Learn animal habitat, character, babies and life-Study animal on the Wikipedia page-Appreciate the animals and beautiful natureA portable animal encyclopedia, zoo, animal TV, animal game!You'll love the Panda, bear, Lion, Orca, Beluga, Hummingbirds, and colorful tropical fish.  Enjoy the animal sounds and high quality pictures and video. Spent time with your kids, read about the animal from the Wikipedia page, watch the hand picked, educational and entertaining high quality free YouTube video from BBC Wildlife, PBS Nature, Animal Planet, Disney and other valuable source. Meet the animals from the all over world and travel with the animal to their native countries in China, Australia, Europe and Africa.  We spent a lots of time screen the YouTube videos and picked the top two for each animal and we watched it from beginning to end and make sure it is kids friendly and offers the best value.Features: -Great selection of 64 creatures, a lots of sea creatures  and birds-Links to wikipedia page of each animal-Hand picked top two kids friendly YouTube videos for each animal from Disney, BBC wildlife, Animal planet... -Great colorful pictures-Great animal sounds-Educational and Entertaining-Swipe back and forth to see the next and previous creature and listen to the animal sound-Click on YouTube icon to see YouTube and Wikipedia links, clik again the links will disappear.-Install on SD card by default, also Movable to SD cardLearn Animals, appreciate the beauty of the nature.  No other App like this, majority of animal Apps only has static animal pictures and static pictures can only do so much.  This App offers rich top quality hand picked animal videos.  Inspire, Educate and Entertain is the best summarize of the App.  Is there anything more interesting than animals for kids?

reviews.title: Works great on Droid X
reviews.comment: Excellent app for little children. It shows the picture of the animal, the name, and the sound the animal makes. In addition, it gives you the option of going to youtube and watching the animal in video. Really fun. I recommend. Thank you for a job well done. The best part, it\'s free!
